A restaurant prepares these types of dishes. We have to make the OO diagram of these.

First Approach


       interface Food
            - collectItemsForDish()
            - prepareDish()
            - garnishDish()


       class Rice : Food {
             override fun collectItemsForDish() {
             }
       }

       class Chole : Food {
       }



        class FoodFactory {

            fun returnFoodObject() : Food{

            if(type == "Rice") {
                   return Rice()
                }
            }


        }




